name: Prefab
description: Represents a prefab object that can be instantiated in the map. Currently handles single elements, not children.

instanceFields.label: AssetType
instanceFields.description: The type of the prefab asset.

instanceFields.label: Asset
instanceFields.description: The asset path/name of the prefab.

instanceFields.label: Static
instanceFields.description: Whether the prefab is marked as static.

instanceFields.label: Position
instanceFields.description: The position of the prefab in world space.

instanceFields.label: Rotation
instanceFields.description: The rotation of the prefab in euler angles.

instanceFields.label: CollideMode
instanceFields.description: The collision mode of the prefab.

instanceFields.label: CollideWith
instanceFields.description: The layers that this prefab can collide with.

instanceFields.label: PhysicsMaterial
instanceFields.description: The name of the physics material applied to the prefab.

instanceFields.label: PersistsOwnership
instanceFields.description: If true and this prefab is spawned at runtime with networking, the ownership will transfer to host if the player who spawned it leaves.

instanceMethods.label: ClearComponents
instanceMethods.description: Clears all components from the prefab.

constructors.description: Creates a new empty Prefab instance.

parameters.name: prefabCSV
parameters.description: The serialized CSV string describing the prefab.

parameters.name: clearComponents
parameters.description: If true, clears all components from the prefab.

constructors.description: Creates a new Prefab instance from a serialized CSV string.
